 No, not I, said the other; 
because I have laid my hand to the 
Plow.


He hath given me rest, by his sorrow; 
and life, by his death . 

CHRISTIAN MEETS THREE SHINING ONES.

 Yes, but that is but seldom; 

but they are to me Golden hours,
in which such things happens to me.
